Examples

library(tidyverse)
library(LFQService)
data <- LFQService::ionstar$normalized()

data$data <- data$data %>% dplyr::filter(protein_Id %in% sample(protein_Id, 100))
res <- medpolish_protein_quants(data$data,
data$config )

#> starting aggregation
